  <h2>How it Works</h2><br>
  <p style="font-size:24px">
    Students and mentor-donors must create an account and a basic profile, with an attached wishlist, on which the student places screenshots of the items' prices, as per the vendor website. The student's profile will then be visible to mentor-donors who have signed up and are looking to sponsor a student or students. In order to sponsor a student, simply Square the donation to bookertapp.washington@gmail.com and state the name and email address of the student as the message (as well as any kind words!). To give a general donation (and thus qualify for tax-exempt status), go to the Donate to the BookerT Fund page.
  </p>
